        <h1 class="page-title" data-title="District Outlines Process for Refunds of Student Fees due to COVID 19 Cancellations"><noscript>District Outlines Process for Refunds of Student Fees due to COVID 19 Cancellations</noscript></h1>
        <aside class="breadcrumbs"><a href="/" class="parent-breadcrumb">Home:</a><a class="child-breadcrumb" href="https://edmondschools.net/news/">News</a></aside><div class="logo-block">
  <a href="/">
    <div class="logo-wrapper">
        <div style="background-image: url('/dist/images/eps-logo.png');"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="logo-text">
